    "It is the most critical element, as the quality and relevance of the chatbot's responses heavily depend on the information and context provided by the prompt.",
    "However, a part of the prompt influences how the human engages with the chatbot since it sets the stage for their expectations from the conversation.",
    "Designing the optimal prompt is challenging, given the nuances of human language and the need to account for numerous conversational scenarios.",
    "Consequently, extensive testing and fine-tuning are necessary to identify the appropriate balance of context, specificity, and flexibility to achieve the desired performance (Zamfirescu-Pereira et al., 2023).",
